---
name: Publish alphaMountain Threats Feed
description: |
  An example that periodically fetches the alphaMountain Threats Feed and
  publishes it to the `alphamountain` topic.
---

every 1h {
  alphamountain::threat::feed_csv license="ALPHAMOUNTAIN_LICENSE",
    risk_min=8.5,
    risk_max=10.0
}
publish "alphamountain"
